{"tid":1962561,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"部相機發咗霉","createTime":"2020-04-07T14:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T19:20:56.000Z","uid":295532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"155396737e9d25e062b40cf1ae9d0912827ea48f","tid":1962561,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"部nikon有年幾冇用過，放喺膠造嘅防潮箱，過年後換咗啲防潮珠，見佢濕度一直50%就冇理佢。<br />\n<br />\n今日執野時開一開個箱，發現機身發咗霉，孭機條帶、鏡頭外啲膠邊有霉菌，有啲係絲狀嘅霉黎，想問點清，係咪用火酒抹咗之後都會生返<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試過影過相，張相就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外相機mon個LCD貼好似氧化咗，有一忽最表面個層玻璃崩咗，即係好似撞崩手機MON貼個啲，想請問外面揾人貼過塊要幾錢？<br />\n<br />\n相機係nikon既D7200，在線等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7263f9bb92c8f58371e7ae553a9f821abc1fa2dd","tid":1962561,"uid":169944,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"掉左個膠盒同部機。出去買個電子箱同部新機"},{"pid":"f3e528527dd09a7ff5f858401640eceb22c80930","tid":1962561,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7263f9bb92c8f58371e7ae553a9f821abc1fa2dd","tid":1962561,"uid":169944,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"掉左個膠盒同部機。出去買個電子箱同部新機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"去到咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b066d8489b07db48048356c0590a271930cdea82","tid":1962561,"uid":169944,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f3e528527dd09a7ff5f858401640eceb22c80930","tid":1962561,"uid":295532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid